extendedInfo.description: The e-Boks app enables you to use e-Boks from all Android-powered devices (smartphones and tablets).You can: * read your documents in horisonzal and landscape view* move and archive documents * create, move and edit folders * subscribe and unsubscribe for new mail from private companies * upload your own pictures from your camera and gallery * edit your profile settings (profile name, e-mail and Danish mobile phone number) In order to log on to the e-Boks app, you need to be a registered user of e-Boks and to activate mobile access from the website http://www.e-boks.dk using NemID. Enter the activation code the first time you access e-Boks from the app.Afterwards you access your e-Boks using only your Danish civil registration number and a password of minimum 6 characters of your own choice.
